  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your wood-fired grill to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Rinse the tiger prawns and pat dry with paper towels.",
    "Season the prawns with Vietnamese chili flakes, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Grill the prawns for 2-3 minutes per side, or until they turn pink and are cooked through.",
    "Meanwhile, warm the baguette by wrapping it in foil and heating it on the grill for 2-3 minutes.",
    "Spread mayonnaise on the bottom half of the baguette.",
    "Add pickled carrots and daikon on top of the mayonnaise.",
    "Place the grilled prawns on top of the vegetables.",
    "Squeeze a sliver of lime juice over the prawns.",
    "Sprinkle chopped cilantro on top of the prawns.",
    "Place the top half of the baguette on the sandwich.",
    "Cut the sandwich in half and serve immediately."
